Package rbvs.record

Interface IInvoice

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Invoice
    public interface IInvoice
    Defines the behavior of an invoice. The interface allows to associate the invoice with a number of IShoppingCartElements and a corresponding PaymentTransaction for them.
    Author:
    OOP
